latestPosts.caption:
This studio isn’t just a dream come true-it’s a labor of love, passion, and endless hard work.

Built from countless hours of dedication, each corner of this space reflects my journey, my struggles, and my belief in the power of beauty to inspire confidence.

At Ellie’s, it’s more than makeup-it’s about celebrating you. 
Whether it’s for a life-changing moment or a simple reminder of your unique glow, 
I’m here to make every transformation special and personal.

I welcome you to step into my dream, and let’s create magic together. ❤️

It’s Officially OPEN!!

25th December 2024! ❤️

@studio04am brought me on board to create a fun transformational look for @leonardhansda for his latest music video. They wanted a rugged yet soft curly-haired style for him—quite the shift from his naturally straight, shoulder-length hair, complementing the dreamy, dewy vibe of the set. After reviewing a few reference looks they sent, I met @leonardhasda on set to understand his preferences and ensure we landed the perfect balance so we could tailor the look to suit him best. Here’s how it all came together.
